This SCP is inspired in no small part by Stargate (the 1994 movie) and the  DVD extra by Kamachi Kazuma.

Do you think the Russian Sputnik is really the first artificial satellite? I've been wondering if it's not possible for the older civilization to reach the space. There are all kind of rocket fuels, but one of them is the Ethanol-Oxygen mixture that the ancient civilizations might realistically produce on their own, given stable economy and source of sugar. Of course, material engineering to produce a frame that could survive launch and knowledge of orbital mechanics are harder to come by, but the point is that it's not strictly impossible for them to create such feats.

I would like to thank Gabriel Jade for giving their general thought and criticism on the article. Y'all are awesome.

Thanks for reading and I hope you enjoy this article!







